OL,3,CCreeslough Justice 'only can be
OL,4,Cprovided through courts', Says
OL,5,CO'Callaghan
OL,7,FThe Irish Justice Minister has said
OL,8,Fhis job was not to be sensitive, but
OL,9,Fto ensure that justice was delivered,
OL,10,Fwhen asked if his refusal to meet
OL,11,Ffamilies affected by the Creeslough
OL,12,Ftragedy was insensitive.
OL,14,FThe Irish Minister for Justice Jim
OL,15,FO'Callaghan said "the only way justice
OL,16,Fcan be provided to (Creeslough
OL,17,Ffamilies) is through the courts."
OL,26,@xD@TpmyD@Ipn
