OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772549422
OL,3,CCreeslough Justice 'only can be
OL,4,Cprovided through courts', Says
OL,5,CO'Callaghan
OL,7,FFour men, three women and three young
OL,8,Fpeople, aged between five and 59, died
OL,9,Fin the blast on the afternoon of
OL,10,FOctober 7, 2022 in the Co Donegal
OL,11,Fvillage.
OL,13,FMinister O'Callaghan was questioned on
OL,14,FMonday by UTV about his refusal to
OL,15,Fmeet the families of the victims.
OL,17,FHe said: "I'm the Minister for
OL,18,FJustice. I want to ensure that the
OL,19,Ffamilies of Creeslough get justice.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772549422
OL,3,CCreeslough Justice 'only can be
OL,4,Cprovided through courts', Says
OL,5,CO'Callaghan
OL,7,F"My job is not to be sensitive. My job
OL,8,Fis to ensure that justice is delivered.
OL,10,F"We're at the very advanced stage of
OL,11,Fthe criminal investigation. A file has
OL,12,Fbeen provided to the DPP.
OL,14,F"My understanding is that a further
OL,15,Ffile would be provided and then the
OL,16,Fcriminal prosecutions are initiated.
OL,18,F"I think that process is the only way
OL,19,Fto which justice can be provided to
OL,20,Fthe families."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
