OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772549422
OL,3,CCreeslough Justice 'only can be
OL,4,Cprovided through courts', Says
OL,5,CO'Callaghan
OL,7,FReacting to Minister O'Callaghan's
OL,8,Fcomments, Donna Harper who lost her
OL,9,Fdaughter Leona in the blast said she
OL,10,Fwas 'hurt' and 'upset.'
OL,12,F"It's very hard to put into words that
OL,13,Fstatement came out from the Minister
OL,14,Fof Justice because it was such a mass
OL,15,Floss of life," she said.
OL,17,FOn Friday, families of Creeslough
OL,18,Fexplosion's victims hit out at the
OL,19,FIrish Justice Minister for rejecting a
OL,20,Frequest to meet with them.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
