OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772549422
OL,3,CCreeslough Justice 'only can be
OL,4,Cprovided through courts', Says
OL,5,CO'Callaghan
OL,7,FRelatives campaigning for a public
OL,8,Finquiry requested a meeting with
OL,9,FMinister O'Callaghan but described his
OL,10,Frefusal as a "slap in the face".
OL,12,FIn December, Minister O'Callaghan met
OL,13,Fwith families to hear their concerns
OL,14,Fbut declined a further meeting to
OL,15,F"allow criminal proceedings to be
OL,16,Fcompleted".
